description:
Doctor Stephen Vincent Strange M.D., Ph.D. was the Sorcerer Supreme and a Master of the Mystic Arts during a time paradox. He was separated from an alternate version of himself by the Ancient One and was tasked with stopping him from breaking an Absolute Point. He was ultimately defeated and absorbed into the corrupted Strange.
